## Frontend Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and customize for your deployment.

```
# Backend API URL (Render deployment)
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com/api/v1

# Development (uncomment for local)
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api/v1

# Google Analytics (optional)
VITE_GA_ID=UA-XXXXX-X

# Sentry (optional)
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=https://xxxxx.ingest.sentry.io/xxxxx
```

**Render Deployment:**
1. In Render Frontend dashboard → Environment
2. Add `VITE_API_URL` = `https://your-backend-service.onrender.com/api/v1`

**Usage:** Frontend `src/lib/api.ts` automatically uses `VITE_API_URL`.

